13. What can you do to save a programme from crashing if it encounters an error?

by debugging the error
by using try and except clause to run and handle the errors 

14. What is the purpose of the try clause? What is the purpose of the except clause?
 
 The try clause helps  in running the code for errors
 The except clause helps in handling the error

